text: Abdul Wahab is a Bangladesh Awami League politician and the former Member of Parliament of Chittagong-5. ==Career== Wahab was elected to parliament from Chittagong-5 as a Bangladesh Awami League candidate in 1973. ==Death== Wahab died on 29 October 2011. ==References== Category:Awami League politicians Category:1st Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing Category:2011 deaths
title: Abdul Wahab (Awami League politician)
